# Refactor UoW

## Trigger Checklist

- User asks to refactor transactions, fix Unit of Work behavior, or clean up transaction boundaries.
- `Rule Guard` finds a `docs/rules/transactions.md` violation.
- A service overlaps remote IO with an active DB transaction.
- A read-only flow starts a transaction without a documented exception.

## Enforce

- Move remote verification or fetch before `Begin()`.
- Keep the transaction around the smallest local atomic write block.
- Repositories share `IDapperContext`; they never own transactions.
- Prefer outbox writes for cross-system side effects.
- Re-audit against `docs/rules/transactions.md`.

